About Me

Welcome to my personal website! My name is Alex Wastl, and I am passionate about web development and technology.

Background

I have a background in computer science and have been working in the tech industry for several years. My expertise includes front-end development, back-end development, and everything in between.

Interests

  • Web Development
  • Open Source Projects
  • Artificial Intelligence
  • Cloud Computing

Contact

Feel free to reach out to me via email@example.com or connect with me on LinkedIn.
